title: Amana Levee FY14
description: The inundation maps in this library submission have been prepared in accordance with the Federal Guidelines for Dam Safety (FEMA Publication 64, FEMA 2004) to identify and delineate areas that could be affected by flooding in the event of a dam failure. The inundation maps support the dam owner and emergency management officials to facilitate timely notification and evacuation of areas affected by a dam failure or flood condition.
